Just curious if the team has discussed allowing an optional biometric factor (fingerprint, facial recognition, etc) for account asset extraction — just an added security feature for those who want it. 

Might that be included somewhere later in the development roadmap?

@SW4GN3R Hi, I have two "simple" questions.

1 - We know that there are female usturs, but so far none have been released in a pack. How will this entry of characters happen? Will there be an appearance "reroll" or will it be limited to unopened packs?

2 - Regarding weapons, in the stories there are katanas among other things that are not in the game. Will this come to the game as well? Will we have some kind of crossbow?
